title: [Fayhlia's Fineries, Southwest]
description: Small orbs of crystal dangling on fine silver chains drape in a staggered swag along the top of the large window here.  Sunlight touches them, splashing dabs of brilliant color upon every surface within reach.

Small orbs of crystal dangling on fine silver chains drape in a staggered swag along the top of the large window here.  Moonlight touches them, making them sparkle and wink in the stark night illumination.
